{"tid":609616,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女子戴「光復香港」標語頸巾被裁定藐視法庭  下午判刑","createTime":"2018-03-29T07:32:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T17:08:40.000Z","uid":165456,"like":1,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"814b448dbb8448e140ef41154ae9d80ee85ba64e","tid":609616,"uid":165456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T07:32:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1388602-20180329.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1388602-20180329.htm&d=WtV8rLE4pArhkj3eEZDXmfjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=17e6884d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1388602-20180329.htm&h=01003901\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1388602-20180329.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n前年發生的旺角騷亂，本土民主前線前發言人梁天琦等人否認暴動、煽惑暴動及非法集結等6項罪名。案件早前審訊期間，一名61歲女子因為在法庭延伸部分的大堂，穿戴印有「光復香港」標語的頸巾，主審法官裁定她的行為屬「藐視法庭」，下午在高等法院判刑。<br />\n<br />\n至於梁天琦等人的案件，押後至下月9日在高等法院再提訊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39530f7aac24cca342ae216080ecb5a58e04811","tid":609616,"uid":96,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T07:33:37.000Z","msg":"大陸人影相就放人走唔追究 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32299242cebe143d02623c47d8b6df14cfb4db76","tid":609616,"uid":34010,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T07:35:07.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，讚個法官判得好，光復左香港又唔撚得？"},{"pid":"1462dcee089041bdea11f44be8228a979fbf25c9","tid":609616,"uid":153689,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T07:59:37.000Z","msg":"香港法官同官員一齊on9，葬送香港前途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3a8a2f9420f2b3a0869e077dac5660322d08a9","tid":609616,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:03:30.000Z","msg":"法庭延伸部分的大堂根本不嬲無人理,大把人食野又盛"},{"pid":"6349354b86534dc3a52e2c9ef1817e6417c9a784","tid":609616,"uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:51:21.000Z","msg":"正於高等法院審理的暴動案，早前有一名經常撐黃傘的婆婆，因戴着寫有「光復香港」的頸巾入庭，被法官彭寶琴指稱她展示標語，判婆婆藐視法庭罪成。婆婆今（29日）在高院稱到庭只是想支持年輕人，彭官卻認為婆婆明知頸巾字句內容，又知法庭已下令不能展示標語，判婆婆罰款1000元，3個月內繳付。<br />\n<br />\n婆婆聽取判決後稱，不知道是否交了罰款等於沒有留下刑事記錄，謂自己「唔應該孭依個罪」，故打算上訴。被問及會否繼續到庭，婆婆稱仍會繼續到庭旁庭支持梁天琦及其他被告。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCCC408/2016"},{"pid":"d83eec603429c62b5277822bb5b218118ee46bee","tid":609616,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T14:13:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd39ae6aa9f066425e108767c6f593790c84e9cc","tid":609616,"uid":27038,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T16:17:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/30/001705_17132f9f4cc34dd359b33fbe4f705573.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F001705_17132f9f4cc34dd359b33fbe4f705573.png&h=b843e125&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd70aab82e24aba4f673ebe3970f9a03647103f7","tid":609616,"uid":28563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d83eec603429c62b5277822bb5b218118ee46bee","tid":609616,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T14:13:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T16:23:07.000Z","msg":"你老母個西都比位連登仔自由出入架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb391691fe06abdac7935db93a8bdd1f2cc6bfd","tid":609616,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d83eec603429c62b5277822bb5b218118ee46bee","tid":609616,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":7,"sc